    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "closure feels like just another word for giving up. why should i have to keep struggling and fighting just to reach a point where i finally get to rest? it feels like the \"purpose\" you're talking about is just more suffering for no reason. if the void is inevitable, why is it considered a failure to just accept it and stop the pain now?",
